{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "464bb2ab-6e22-4770-bf2f-658b8093ffbd", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/464bb2ab-6e22-4770-bf2f-658b8093ffbd@1.pkg/1772597681376/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597681963", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/464bb2ab-6e22-4770-bf2f-658b8093ffbd@1.pkg/1772597681376/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597681963"}, "identifier": "464bb2ab-6e22-4770-bf2f-658b8093ffbd", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查对 &ldquo;家的意味&rdquo; 的理解。​</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>A：春运中人们千里归家，正是因为家能给予心灵的温暖与情感的归宿，符合题意。​</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>B：家的核心是情感寄托，而非财富获取，与春运体现的对家的情感向往不符。​</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>C：家的意义不在于炫耀成就，该说法偏离了家的本质内涵。​</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>D：春运体现的是人们对家的主动向往和情感依赖，而非被动的法律责任。​</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>故选为A。</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（原创）中国的春运，无数人跨越千里奔向家园，这份对家的执着向往体现出（ ）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（原创）中国的春运，无数人跨越千里奔向家园，这份对家的执着向往体现出（ ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/464bb2ab-6e22-4770-bf2f-658b8093ffbd@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754977891734", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>家是</span><span>我们</span><span>心灵的温暖港湾​</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>家是赚取财富的重要场所​</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>家是展示成就的炫耀平台​</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>家是必须履行的法律责任</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（原创）中国的春运，无数人跨越千里奔向家园，这份对家的执着向往体现出（ ）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "